Planning / Considering
----------------------

- make nr_accesses same to probe_hits[0]
- Refactor damon API to pass parameters only
  - damon_start() returns only handles that can be used with damon_call().
  - move lifecycle management of running ctx to core
  - steps
    - introduce damon_{enter,exit}_exclusive_mode().
    - replace damon_start() and damon_stop() calls to use __damon_start() and
      __damon_stop().
    - introduce new damon_start() and damon_stop().
    - replace __damon_start() and __damon_stop() to new damon_{start,stop}().
    - example usage:
      param = damon_new_param(essential thing);
      damon_param_add_scheme(...);
      damon_id = damon_start(param, NULL);
      damon_destroy_param(param);
      damon_param new_param;
      damon_init_param(new_param, ...);
      damon_id = damon_start(ne_param, damon_id); /* commit */
      damon_call(damon_id, ...);
      damos_walk(damon_id, ...);
      damon_stop(damon_id);
